{"tid":1481573,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"仲食緊金拱門既你無資格想光復香港","createTime":"2019-08-17T18:21:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-19T01:01:29.000Z","uid":278414,"like":86,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"8667ce7f90e80b893933b00d94cea4b6f586f549","tid":1481573,"uid":278414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T18:21:02.000Z","msg":"罷食 罷買 在長期抗爭中是非常重要<br />\n唔該各位手足由慢慢戒食金拱門開始 直至完全唔食<br />\n唔好同我講好難戒<br />\n連咁簡單既<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>堅持</strong></span></span>都做唔到<br />\n就唔好話想光復香港<br />\n當你作為消費者 將金錢以投票方式支持紅企<br />\n你已經幫緊敵人助攻緊 唔該醒醒<br />\n<br />\n今日仲見到好多2x歲左右既人去食卜野家<br />\n真係屌左出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8e35a31df425cbbf55c4da08e3d435a1cb64dd9","tid":1481573,"uid":63202,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T18:22:58.000Z","msg":"唔食m記 可以食咩<br />\n25蚊就一餐"},{"pid":"87acb3fe8984a6c9f80a8765a5b71e2de02e68f3","tid":1481573,"uid":653,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T18:25:27.000Z","msg":"D手足唔係個個都有錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17b8ce6d7dc71e70dc8be85076d999fcd2ca0306","tid":1481573,"uid":278414,"like":0,"dislike":34,"score":-34,"quote":{"pid":"b8e35a31df425cbbf55c4da08e3d435a1cb64dd9","tid":1481573,"uid":63202,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T18:22:58.000Z","msg":"唔食m記 可以食咩<br />\n25蚊就一餐"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T18:25:33.000Z","msg":"學煮飯啦<br />\n識女仔時又可以加分"},{"pid":"6b52a13eebb387577c3ffea3bdeb4eeea1e6e0cb","tid":1481573,"uid":98465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T18:26:54.000Z","msg":"豬柳強係軍糧"},{"pid":"03474590c942f4940aebcd9534c8761585486b6a","tid":1481573,"uid":278414,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"quote":{"pid":"87acb3fe8984a6c9f80a8765a5b71e2de02e68f3","tid":1481573,"uid":653,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T18:25: