路線。作者解釋社運後來的發展：<br />\n<br />\n「自我反省由於帶着強烈倫理色彩，忠於這些原則的運動者，會去攻擊不如自己認真看待運動的戰友，或是在沒辦法堅持原則的時候感到挫折。運動者無法對戰友採取寬容的態度，導致內部衝突和暴力，太着重於抽象的理念，容易陷入自以為是的危險」。<br />\n<br />\n簡而言之，就是變得太「道德L」「佔領道理高地」，於是社運人士之間有內鬥，更甚者會殺害覺得不夠忠誠的志士。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1283959/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1283959/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"9464875e7aa5f32960c294f0c7b5b66baa53af1c","tid":1481573,"uid":279677,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"4437c0edd7ee9c31f16c9be904ad6c93268029e8","tid":1481573,"uid":282460,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"17b8ce6d7dc71e70dc8be85076d999fcd2ca0306","tid":1481573,"uid":278414,"like":0,"dislike":34,"score":-34,"quote":{"pid":"b8e35a31df425cbbf55c4da08e3d435a1cb64dd9","tid":1481573,"uid":63202,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T18:22:58.000Z","msg":"唔食m記 可以食咩<br />\n25蚊就一餐"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T18:25:33.000Z","msg":"學煮飯啦<br />\n識女仔時又可以加分"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T19:17:52.000Z","msg":"其實自己煮仲撚貴"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T19:50:54.000Z","msg":"屌 呢個真 啲人成日話出街食貴 我心諗點解我自己買餸仲貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"005c9a22ef63c7e18c9bcec7f188cddda8384de0","tid":1481573,"uid":210794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T19:53:13.000Z","msg":"仲有吉野家 大家樂集團旗下"},{"pid":"6cee99d972e1eed09193c9d5c781d324cf1ad6c9","tid":1481573,"uid":61653,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"d5659ff09d2ca9f724fce7fdc79cc89bd8dca16b","tid":1481573,"uid":278414,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"bfe9001ddca5c86e30f8e2fd84bef46800bbb768","tid":1481573,"uid":229369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"03474590c942f4940aebcd9534c8761585486b6a","tid":1481573,"uid":278414,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T18:26:59.000Z","msg":"無錢 未自己煮羅帶飯"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T18:31:49.000Z","msg":"無可能自己帶飯去遊行，甚至上前線"},"cite